The evidence with the title 'Olympic hopefuls seek balance in speaking out, representing country ' says Sep 29, 2017  ... “ it's a delicate balance representing the U.S. and wanting to represent your country well and still wanting to let people know what is going on is not ok , ” ... To be stood up for right now , ” said Olympic silver medalist Gus Kenworthy , who in 2015 became the first action sports athlete to come out publicly as gay . 
